    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it never stops. the physical stuff, the mental stuff, and then seeing them struggle to take care of me. i feel like a weight around their necks. sometimes i just wonder if they'd actually be more at peace if they didn't have to worry about me anymore. if they could just be free of it all.",
